Package org.opensaml.saml.common.messaging.context.navigate

Functions to navigate SAML message contexts.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttributeConsumerServiceLookupFunction
    Function to return the AttributeConsumingService from the AttributeConsumingServiceContext.
    EntityDescriptorLookupFunction
    ContextDataLookupFunction to return the EntityDescriptor from a SAMLMetadataContext.
    SAMLBindingContextBindingFunction
    ContextDataLookupFunction that returns the SAML binding from a SAMLBindingContext.
    SAMLMessageContextAuthenticationFunction
    Function that returns the authenticated state of a configured AbstractAuthenticatableSAMLEntityContext, defaulting to SAMLPeerEntityContext.
    SAMLMessageContextIssuerFunction
    Function that returns the entityID from a SAMLPeerEntityContext or SAMLSelfEntityContext.
    SAMLMessageInfoContextIDFunction
    ContextDataLookupFunction that returns SAMLMessageInfoContext.getMessageId().
    SAMLMessageInfoContextIssueInstantFunction
    ContextDataLookupFunction that returns SAMLMessageInfoContext.getMessageIssueInstant().
    SAMLProtocolContextProtocolFunction
    ContextDataLookupFunction that returns the protocol from a SAMLProtocolContext.
